headline: Acadia Realty Trust (AKR) Q1 FFO and Revenues Top Estimates
summary: Acadia Realty Trust (AKR) delivered FFO and revenue surprises of 3.03% and 6.52%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
